snippet.title: Starlight X-2 Galactic Puzzles: PC Trailer
snippet.description:
Starlight X-2: Galactic Puzzles is a space-themed puzzle game.

The game is available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1575040/Starlight_X2_Galactic_Puzzles/ (free demo available as well)
And on itch.io: https://frozax.itch.io/starlight-x2

A mobile version is also available on Android (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.frozax.starsandasteroids) and iOS (https://apps.apple.com/app/thermometers-puzzles/id1071003654)
